      <p align="center" class="style2">
        The desire to have a safe play area for local children had been
        considered at various times for Westmuir village.&nbsp;&nbsp; The
        resulting transformation of a veritable scrubland into an accessible,
        appealing and attractive village amenity clearly demonstrates what can
        be achieved by harnessing the views of a supportive community with the
        combined enthusiasm and perseverance of a hard working development
        group.
      </p>
      <p align="center" class="style2">
        Click on the links to the
        <a href="Woodland_Opening.html" target="_blank">Woodland Opening</a>,
        the
        <a href="PDF Pages/Tree_Planting_5th_December_2009.pdf" target="_blank"
          >National Tree Planting Day</a
        >
        and a
        <a href="PDF Pages/Activity_Day_June_2009.pdf" target="_blank"
          >Woodland Activity Day</a
        >
        which demonstrate how popular the Community Woodland has become.
      </p>
