    <td align="center" class="style2">
      Thanks to the Westmuir Hall Association and the Westmuir Community
      Development Trust, great progress was made in a relatively short time. A
      Community Futures process was initiated in 2003 with the help of Angus
      Rural Partnership and STAR (Small Town and Rural Development Group). A
      Community Survey issued to all residents was an essential part of this
      process and high on the community plan wish list was &ldquo;Somewhere safe
      for children to play&rdquo;
    </td>
