      <div align="center">
        <p>
          Attractive curved walls have been built at each entrance all thanks to
          the efforts of the local members of the
          <a href="http://dswa.org.uk" target="_blank"
            >Dry Stone Walling Association</a
          >. These have added great character to the village as well as the
          woodland itself.
        </p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
      </div>
    </td>
    <td width="60">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="304" class="style2">
      <div align="center">
        Further improvements by WCDT included the provision of interpretation
        panels at each entrance and large &lsquo;entrance&rsquo; notice. These
        give visitors an insight to what they can expect within the woodland and
        make an attractive addition.
      </div>
    </td>
    <td width="36">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="305" class="style2">
      <div align="center">
        Three well known villagers have gained valuable new skills during this
        project and we will now be able to carry out ongoing maintenance of the
        walling as a result. Why not become involved yourself? Get in touch via
        the
        <a href="Contact_Us.html">Contact Page</a> and offer your help.
      </div>
    </td>
